Radius TV

Having trouble accessing UMN-TV?

Before you ask for help, double check that your wired Ethernet connection is secure for UMN-TV Online, and the TV coaxial cable is secure for cable UMN-TV. If you are still unable to connect to UMN-TV, submit a Connect It request. Please do not contact Comcast/Xfinity.
